title: Kanban Board
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

A kanban board represents work items flowing through status columns. Use it to document sprint state, visualize a workflow, or show task assignments. ''New in Mermaid 11.'' Uses the `kanban` keyword.

---

!! Basic example

```
kanban
  todo[To Do]
    t1[Write unit tests]
    t2[Update changelog]
    t3[Review open PRs]
  doing[In Progress]
    t4[Implement search]
    t5[Fix login bug]
  done[Done]
    t6[Set up CI]
    t7[Deploy v1.0]
```

