!! Real-world example: Sprint board with metadata

```
kanban
  backlog[Backlog]
    b1[Dark mode support]
    b2[CSV export]
    b3[API rate limiting]
  todo[Sprint — To Do]
    t1[OAuth2 integration]@{ assigned: 'alice' }
    t2[Password reset flow]@{ assigned: 'bob' }
  doing[In Progress]
    t3[Refactor auth middleware]@{ assigned: 'alice', ticket: GH-112 }
    t4[Write API docs]@{ assigned: 'carol' }
  review[Review]
    t5[Add dark mode toggle]@{ assigned: 'bob', ticket: GH-98 }
  done[Done]
    t6[Set up staging env]
    t7[Database migrations]
```

